The Nigerian Navy has decried circulation of fake list of successful candidates for its 2019 recruitment exercise. The Director of Information Commodore Suleman Dahun in a statement said the Nigerian Navy has not released list of its successful candidates, adding that the list will be made available to the public through the Nigerian Navy official website and other media platforms. “The Nigerian Navy wishes to alert members of the public of the existence online of a fake list of successful candidates in its 2019 Recruitment Exercise. “For the avoidance of doubt, the Nigerian Navy has not released the list of successful candidates in the 2019 Recruitment Exercise. “Therefore, members of the public are advised to steer clear of these fraudulent sites. “Furthermore, the list of successful candidates will be conveyed to the public in the Nigerian Navy official website and mass media in due course,” he said